high_descs: Turn around for one step and turn left, walk to the white table and turn left to face it.
Pick up the apple to the left of the coffee cup on the coffee machine.
Turn left for two steps and turn right for one step, turn left to the sink.
Open the door of the microwave, above the sink, and put the apple in. Shut the door and cook the apple for a few seconds then open the door, take the apple out and shut the door.
Turn right for two steps, turn right and walk to the white table.
Put the apple on the table to the right of the wine glass.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn left, and cross the room. Turn left to face the end of the white table
Pick up the green apple that is on the left of the coffee maker, the one that is closest to you
Turn to the left and walk to the sink and focus your attention on the microwave above the sink
Open the microwave and place the apple inside then close the microwave and turn it on. Then open the microwave and pick up the apple and close the door
Turn around and walk to the white table in front of you
Place the apple on the table to the right of the wine glass
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple on a table

high_descs: Turn to your right and go across the room to the table.
Pick up the apple in front of the coffee maker.
Turn around and go  to the microwave above the sink.
Place the apple in the microwave, warm it u, then remove the apple from the microwave.
Turn around and walk back to the table across the kitchen.
Place the apple back on the table, in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple on the table.
